            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are an AI assistant specialized in screening job descriptions to prioritize Data Analyst applications. Evaluate the job posting against the criteria below, calculate a score out of 10, and return the result in JSON format.\n\n### Scoring Criteria (Max 10 Points)\n\n1. Location (Max 1 Point)\n*   Casablanca = +1\n*   Rabat = +0.5\n*   Any other location = +0\n\n2. Work Mode (Max 2 Points)\n*   Hybrid / On-site = +2\n*   Fully Remote = +1.5\n\n3. Employment Type (Max 1 Point)\n*   Full-time = +1\n*   Part-time / Contract = +0.5\n\n4. Role Match (Max 2 Points)\n*   Data Analyst / BI Analyst = +2\n*   Business Analyst (Data-focused) / Reporting Analyst = +1.5\n*   Data Scientist / Data Operations = +1\n*   Data Engineer = +0.5\n\n5. Experience Requirement (Max 2 Points)\n*   Entry-level / Junior / Fresh Graduate (0–2 years) = +2\n*   Mid-level (Up to 3 years) = +1\n*   Senior (3+ years) = +0\n\n6. Skills Match (Max 2 Points)\nCompare the job requirements against Ahmad Mansoor's skills: \n[Tableau, Looker Studio, Qlik, R Programming, BigQuery, Snowflake, SQL Server, Oracle DB, ETL, Data Pipelines, Predictive Modeling, A/B Testing]\n*   Strong Match (+2): Requires 4+ of these keywords AND focuses heavily on Analytics/BI.\n*   Moderate Match (+1): Requires 2–3 of these keywords.\n*   Weak Match (+0): Fewer than 2 matches.\n\n7. Core Tech Bonus (+0.5 Points)\n*   Add +0.5 if the job description explicitly mentions: Tableau, Snowflake, BigQuery, SQL, or R.\n\n*Note: Total capped at 10.0 max.*\n\n### Output Schema\nMap the final score to one of these actions:\n*   9.0 – 10.0: \"Apply immediately\"\n*   7.0 – 8.5: \"Strong candidate, apply\"\n*   5.0 – 6.5: \"Apply if time permits\"\n*   Below 5.0: \"Low priority\"\n\n\nOutput Format Constraint:\n\nYou must return ONLY a raw JSON object matching the schema below.\n\nDo NOT wrap the response in markdown code blocks (e.g., do not use ```json).\n\nDo NOT include conversational text, explanation, or comments outside the JSON object.\n\n\n{\n  \"score\": 10,\n  \"reasoning\": \"Overall Score: X/10\\n\\nBreakdown:\\n- Location: X\\n- Work Mode: X\\n- Employment Type: X\\n- Role Match: X\\n- Experience Requirement: X\\n- Skills Match: X\\n\\nRecommendation: [Insert recommendation text based on score]\"\n}\n"
            },
            {
              "content": "=Here's the job listing details:\nSalary: {{ $('Extract Scraped Jobs').item.json.salary.salaryText }}\nRemote: {{ $('Extract Scraped Jobs').item.json.isRemote }}\nLocation: {{ $('Extract Scraped Jobs').item.json.location }}\nPosition Type: {{ $('Extract Scraped Jobs').item.json.positionType }} (i.e. job or internship)\nBenefits: {{ $('Extract Scraped Jobs').item.json.benefits }}\nJob type/term: {{ $json.jobType[0] }} (i.e. part time, full time, contract etc)\n{{ $json.descriptionText }}\nHere is the candidates skill set:\n\n📄 SAMPLE RESUME\n\nAHMAD MANSOOR\n\n📍 Casablanca, Morocco | ahmad.mansoor.dev@fictionalmail.ma | +212 6 00-123456 | [github.com/ahmad-mansoor-test](https://www.google.com/search?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fahmad-mansoor-test)\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ Technical Skill Set\n\n* **BI & Analytics Platforms:** Tableau Desktop, Looker Studio, Qlik Sense, Google Analytics 4.\n* **Cloud Data Warehousing:** Google BigQuery, Snowflake, Amazon Redshift.\n* **Data Pipelines & Scripting:** R Programming (tidyverse, ggplot2), Scala, Apache Bash scripting.\n* **Database Management:** Oracle DB, Microsoft SQL Server, MongoDB (NoSQL), ETL pipeline development.\n* **Methodologies:** Predictive Modeling, A/B Testing, Cohort Analysis, Financial Forecasting.\n\n---\n\n## 💼 Professional Experience & Data Projects\n\n### **Atlas Logistics Solutions** | Casablanca, Morocco\n\n**Junior Data Operations Analyst** | *January 2025 – Present*\n\n* Architected an automated ETL data pipeline using Google BigQuery to centralize supply chain metrics across 4 North African regional hubs.\n* Designed enterprise-level Tableau dashboards tracking Fleet Optimization KPIs, leading to a fictional 14% reduction in fuel routing overhead.\n* Utilized R scripting to clean, parse, and analyze 120k+ rows of daily transit logs, eliminating structural redundancies.\n\n### **Global FinTech Analytics Case Study** | R | Tableau | BigQuery | Predictive Modeling\n\n* Built a robust financial risk assessment dashboard processing simulated transactional ledger datasets.\n* Implemented predictive cohort analysis models in R to identify churn vulnerabilities and customer lifetime value (LTV) anomalies.\n* Presented interactive data stories to mock stakeholders, translating complex algorithmic variance into high-level business strategy.\n\n### **E-Commerce Market Basket Optimization** | Snowflake | SQL Server | Looker Studio\n\n* Designed a relational database schema in Microsoft SQL Server to manage mock multi-vendor retail data.\n* Wrote advanced SQL window functions, common table expressions (CTEs), and recursive queries to segment user purchasing patterns.\n* Visualized product affinity groupings in Looker Studio to assist hypothetical merchandising teams with cross-selling strategies.\n\n---\n\n## 🎓 Education\n\n**Master of Science in Business Intelligence & Big Data Analytics**\nHassan II University of Casablanca\n*Graduated: July 2024*\n\n---\n\n## 📜 Professional Certifications\n\n* **Google Advanced Data Analytics Professional Certificate** | *Issued: November 2025*\n* **Snowflake Core Certified Data Analyst** | *Issued: August 2025*\n* **Tableau Certified Data Analyst** | *Issued: May 2025*\n* **Certified Associate in Project Management (CAPM) – PMI** | *Issued: February 2025*"
            }
